    "clusterId": "0b72f60c-7a4b-40fb-9c64-11795d64bf43",
    "text": "Trump called Anthropic 'Leftwing nut jobs' and said they made a 'DISASTROUS MISTAKE trying to STRONG-ARM the Department of War'",
    "status": "undisputed",
    "supportingSources": [
      "Ars Technica"
    ],
    "disputingSources": [],
